data.description: Offering $5000 to closing cost or interest rates with preferred lender! This perfect two-story home is 2910 sq ft with 5 bedrooms, 3.1 baths and 2 car garage. Beautiful flooring and crown molding in living area, kitchen and formal dining. Wood burning fire place in living area and custom build shelves through out the home.  Pretty white painted cabinets in kitchen with granite countertops and a cute breakfast nook.  Primary bedroom and bath on first floor with nice tile separate shower and garden tub with a large primary closet. The upstairs has a game room with movie projector or could be used as second living area. There are 4 bedrooms upstairs with 2 full baths that have tiled showers and tubs. Lots of closet space and storage! This home sits on a large corner lot in a wonderful neighborhood. There is a community pool, clubhouse, and playground.  Great location off HWY 114 and in Northwest ISD! Don't miss out on this home!
